OL,4,CBig rise in numbers of migrant children
OL,5,Con Mexico-US border
OL,6, The number of migrant children trying
OL,7, to reach the US from Mexico has
OL,8, increased ninefold since the start of
OL,9, 2021, UN children's agency Unicef says.
OL,11,FThe rise from 380 to nearly 3,500 has
OL,12,Foverwhelmed the facilities at Mexico's
OL,13,Freception centres, it says.
OL,15,FThe children are mainly from Honduras,
OL,16,FGuatemala, El Salvador and Mexico
OL,17,Fitself. Half arrived without parents.
OL,19,FNearly 300 children are added to their
OL,20,Fnumber every day, as they wait to cross
OL,21,Finto the US or are sent back.
